{"tid":1567390,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［悲觀慎入］沈旭暉主持既《人權法》研討會咁重要無人討論？","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:15:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:17:18.000Z","uid":39021,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"c4266374175cd58de1dedbc1f8f8e3c7555796cd","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/videos/916713948707471/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%2Fvideos%2F916713948707471%2F&d=CilPfclB3esq2vqCdqPDZ%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=77e004cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon/videos/916713948707471/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實好多地方值得討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沈旭暉只係負責提供facts同backgrounds，無直接提出意見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>與會者對人權法作用較悲觀</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>黃詩朗（政政博士）：</strong></span><br />\n認為民間吹大咗《香港人權與民主法案》，實際上殺傷力極細<br />\n《香港關係法》一直都容許取消香港關係法，《人權法》同《香港關係法》分別不大，其實唔係咩新野<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（沈旭暉補充：《人權法》重新要求政府每年提供report，令report更重要）</span><br />\n<ins>唔見得中央會因為美國制裁幾個香港官員而改變對港政策</ins><span style=\"font-size: small;\">（沈旭暉補充：《人權法》或令美國承認其對香港既直接影響）</span><br />\n提及Rubio提出過，《香港關係法》只有延續同取消兩個選項，太難用，<ins>《人權法》旨在加多少少傷害不大既選項（制裁官員），多咗空間比美國政府表態</ins><br />\n只有中美關係極決裂，先有可能取消《香港關係法》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>鍾國斌：</strong></span><br />\n《人權法》只有心理作用，無實際作用，<ins>同佢會面既四位美國議員亦都係同一諗法</ins><br />\n通過機會高，但未必立即討論，因為<ins>林鄭撤咗逃犯條例，美國議員立即Whatsapp恭喜佢</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n類似制裁官員措施其實主要攻擊對像係第三世界獨栽官員，香港情況唔同，因為香港官員做唔得長（並非長命獨栽，制裁影響有限），同時香港官員同美國政府較相熟，好難動用制裁，所以作用有限<br />\n聲稱自己非常熟美國人性格，因為同美國人做咗三十年生意，認為美國佬講就天下無敵，做就碌撚<br />\n<ins>美國每年從香港賺300億以上美元，利益極大，最少五年內唔會取消《香港關係法》，總商會亦會不斷lobby美國政府叫政府唔好搞香港</ins><br />\n香港官員應該主動lobby美國政府，表達《人權法》根本無大作用<br />\n<ins>會面既四位美國議員話根本唔想搞香港，但香港搞唔掂的話，佢地就要介入</ins><br />\n真係有效果既只係《香港關係法》，而唔係《人權法》，但美國無興趣同香港攬炒，唔會郁《香港關係法》<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>陳雲：</strong></span><br />\n（遲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />講野慢同長，講咗一次就俾大灣暉截停）<br />\n對資產階級黎講，法律係鬥爭工具，美國就同你借《人權法》玩法律鬥爭<br />\n認為美國政治攻擊非常subtle，體現係最近已經要求中資交待高層政治背景，呢類攻擊無約束力亦不是直接懲罰，殺傷力「係唔知道，唔可以講有定無」<br />\n美國制裁香港官員影響力有幾大係「睇情況」，若美國制裁香港官員，中國會變得尷尬，如果外交部出聲就代表香港官員係中國官員，唔出聲就比人踩到上心口都無聲出<br />\n美國好多野都好多uncertainty，uncertainty係鬥爭常用技巧，<ins>形容《人權法》加埋其他野一齊用，會係雞尾酒醫療法，有用既</ins><br />\n唔好理《人權法》有無用，爭取咗先，中共係美國既敵人，但香港同美國唔係敵人亦唔係朋友，<ins>如果《人權法》真係無用，繼續鬥落去，因為已經進入「可持續鬥爭」狀態</ins><br />\n全球鬥爭界都認為美國係敵人，但今次認為美國《人權法》做得好"},{"pid":"e1cd38943c789aff5b38ee86fccebe4decd99279","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04d5787bd7667409d69fafb71a735363a2884c9","tid":1567390,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b01c4bf4ac2a4d21b639dbf23dcc20e99d8187","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n美國每年從香港<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淨</span></strong>賺300億以上美元"},{"pid":"c07436cafaca9244278d98dabcff46eb798c2352","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:18:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e6882a1d567fb125172bca7062942532ff625e","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97461e0c3631f193f37afba596c987ca1eaa0e8","tid":1567390,"uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:20:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n其實要諗如果過唔到/無用，仲有咩對策<br />\n我認為國際方向正確<br />\n但唔可以只係美國<br />\n要向埋歐盟的國家<br />\n輸出如果香港失去自治<br />\n將會損害埋佢地的利益"},{"pid":"d313c74840471a6f3b9aaf0a32bf389e76a7dd35","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beae30ca74d60fdaf66695fc8fb235c21a9e1806","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5578516f597d9d9cc11c80d4909a7709b46ce35b","tid":1567390,"uid":41963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:24:03.000Z","msg":"有法案就有喘息空間<br />\n冇法案就萬劫不復"},{"pid":"69c0b7e2a025cce1356497c9b2371f5a8c438295","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e483c3417350dd7fab6c87e0767ad360530a4e1","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"782f62b227e217b3309bae9cda4bd1c53e382d82","tid":1567390,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:26:44.000Z","msg":"咩都好緊係爭取左先"},{"pid":"dcdcf934ce770e1278af0bc51bdcff9fe92d4f6c","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b54f42f5941fc9b0fdb9dae6ff38767ff2103f","tid":1567390,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b01c4bf4ac2a4d21b639dbf23dcc20e99d8187","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:18:01.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n美國每年從香港<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">淨</span></strong>賺300億以上美元"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:28:56.000Z","msg":"又或者咁諗，要諗美國公司為香港，提供幾多就業機會稅收科技等等。<br />\n<br />\n如果單純數字，美國一世唔會取消關係法。但取消關係法，只要可以搵個地方，做返香港既工作，咁美國取消關係法，佢地唔會介意。"},{"pid":"41794819af6c3bb4ca06b9adf22e9045eedea8cb","tid":1567390,"uid":265179,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"一步步爭取, 人權法只係其中一關, 所以話呢個係長期抗爭. 個D成日話一鋪定輸贏, 實在太唔了解實際情況.."},{"pid":"37bfd080d1ae0bc5a14670b90d2960be2f0c35d8","tid":1567390,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"未詳細聽，但睇你復述，黃詩朗同鐘國斌可以不理，前者基本上唔知《人權法》嘅立法意圖，係補充香港關係法，後者立場問題，當然會唱淡，更加唔洗理。"},{"pid":"edcd707926ad278e0f71f03c3731942cb01b5f20","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470b31119a22a4e63354b7416ade47a1d8cc5e57","tid":1567390,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">香港官員應該主動lobby美國政府，表達《人權法》根本無大作用<br />\n會面既四位美國議員話根本唔想搞香港，但香港搞唔掂的話，佢地就要介入</span><br />\n<br />\n港共真係咁諗，所以佢地出盡力拉，又 ban 晒所有遊行，係想冇焦點係香港。<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要繼續追究831 同 721恐襲，呢啲人道災難，港共冇得兜，而且國際冇藉口唔理。上到國會討論，就算奶共既議員，都冇藉口唔處理。"},{"pid":"84cc6fee12ef4a401770f025bb3e52ed087c1ea8","tid":1567390,"uid":30988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:38:46.000Z","msg":"其實睇支國一路嘅國策，<br />\n已經知會點對應<br />\n<br />\n不要妄想可以用人權法就能得到人權。<br />\n要思考的是如何利用該法制裁官員，<br />\n長期通過制裁維持國際關係，同抗爭壓力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81de31705cf1fc929d2264bb5c469ec1d3c4bc7","tid":1567390,"uid":204429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"個班官緊係話冇用啦 美國帶頭制裁 美國打下嘅國家同城市都會跟住一齊制裁 形成全球制裁中國"},{"pid":"529637e358342a404d1173dc268344d8156ab2e4","tid":1567390,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:40:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"63f133dd6d3d0a6b6e52c3edd837be36dc5be7cb","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a1585a9fa035593beab8154661b8af77293b89","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37bfd080d1ae0bc5a14670b90d2960be2f0c35d8","tid":1567390,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"未詳細聽，但睇你復述，黃詩朗同鐘國斌可以不理，前者基本上唔知《人權法》嘅立法意圖，係補充香港關係法，後者立場問題，當然會唱淡，更加唔洗理。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"黃詩朗好似唔好明做緊乜咁，大灣暉連忙同佢補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但鐘國斌真係唔似係因為立場而唱淡"},{"pid":"a1196389e57d9dbab73c2319947904141510522e","tid":1567390,"uid":292798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"啲人因為有陳雲而唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n等陳雲打手全面進場中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7065c034c4f879c3a325b6e31f1523f1c86d1893","tid":1567390,"uid":86090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"97a1585a9fa035593beab8154661b8af77293b89","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37bfd080d1ae0bc5a14670b90d2960be2f0c35d8","tid":1567390,"uid":196430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:30:39.000Z","msg":"未詳細聽，但睇你復述，黃詩朗同鐘國斌可以不理，前者基本上唔知《人權法》嘅立法意圖，係補充香港關係法，後者立場問題，當然會唱淡，更加唔洗理。"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:43:11.000Z","msg":"黃詩朗好似唔好明做緊乜咁，大灣暉連忙同佢補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但鐘國斌真係唔似係因為立場而唱淡"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"唔通親中派話好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩"},{"pid":"cfb4e21d9c824ddedd162829f2c4af875ee3ea8d","tid":1567390,"uid":2816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"「認為民間吹大咗《香港人權與民主法案》，實際上殺傷力極細」<br />\n<br />\n認同呢點,始終只係一個起步點,不抱太大期望<br />\n但同時係一個好開始,可以比香港人繼續爭取更多既支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2c73a7fb10b49d27af5a6bd44ea90e97086d12c","tid":1567390,"uid":300718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:48:22.000Z","msg":"唔好等到十一，入黎打長期戰。<br />\n<br />\n【新主線：民間遞進民主平台】<br />\n<br />\n盡用人數優勢，以民主爭取民主，打長期戰。邀請有心巴絲加入策劃<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566855\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566855</a>"},{"pid":"8fad1f328276459c6a79c3ee2fb9276b1564c607","tid":1567390,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7065c034c4f879c3a325b6e31f